  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-03 stale dataset)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. A model revision was performed in 2026 incorporating updated turbulence closure coefficients and revised impeller geometry; however, the primary experimental validation dataset retains a 2018 vintage and was not re-collected or re-processed following the revision. The narrative does not address re-validation against the updated model build.",
